Get out of here.
Come on, out of here.

04:05.487 --> 04:06.856
Hey, hey, you, hey, hey.

04:06.922 --> 04:08.958
Go take that clothes off.

04:09.024 --> 04:12.828
Come on, you fellas. Get out.
Get the music racks out of here.

