'I don't know.'

49:40.587 --> 49:42.889
I am Faneuil H. Peabody.

49:42.955 --> 49:44.824
- Faneuil?
- Faneuil.

49:44.891 --> 49:47.360
When I know you better,
I'll call you Fanny.

49:47.427 --> 49:49.562
Have you got a cigarette?

49:53.633 --> 49:55.635
Mmm. Gold.

49:57.169 --> 49:58.938
Oh! Oh, my error.

49:59.005 --> 50:00.807
Have you a light?

50:04.511 --> 50:06.879
Mmm. Your hand is shaking.

50:06.946 --> 50:07.947
'Ha ha ha!'

50:08.014 --> 50:09.982
What an unexpected pleasure.

50:10.049 --> 50:13.252
Come along, let's sit over on
the other side of the room.

50:13.320 --> 50:14.721
Come on! Come along.

50:14.787 --> 50:16.756
You know, I used
to know some Peabodys

50:16.823 --> 50:19.258
but I think
they came from Texas.

50:19.326 --> 50:22.662
Aw, sit down, now.
Come on, sit down.

50:22.729 --> 50:24.531
There.

50:24.597 --> 50:28.768
